Short summary:
This is the privacy policy for the app "Luvy - App for Couples". All of the data that is collected in the App will be only saved
locally
on your devices. The data will
not processed by us and not passed on to third parties
.
Only when you contact us, personal data will be transmitted to us. But this data will be only processed by us.
The privacy policy informs you about the processing of your data in accordance with Article 13 of the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) of the European Union.
Structure of the privacy policy
1. Responsible entity
2. Scope of application
3. Legal basis of the processing
4. What personal information is collected and what is it used for?
5. What features of your smartphone does the app Luvy use?
6. How long is your personal data stored?
7. How is your personal data protected?
